38 SECTION 7. The Speaker of the House of Representatives or the President Pro
39 Tempore of the Senate may authorize appropriate committees or subcommittees of their
40 respective houses to meet during the interims between sessions to (i) review matters related to
41 the State budget for the 2025-2027 fiscal biennium, (ii) prepare reports, including revised
42 budgets, or (iii) consider any other matters as the Speaker of the House of Representatives or the
43 President Pro Tempore of the Senate deems appropriate. A conference committee may meet in
44 the interim upon approval by the Speaker of the House of Representatives or the President Pro
45 Tempore of the Senate.
46 SECTION 8. This resolution is effective upon ratification.
